attributes.Long form description:
The student disassembles a rolling cart. He starts by unscrewing the four wheels.
 Afterward, he unscrews the six brackets to be able to take out the trays. He starts with the middle one, changes to the top one, and in the end the bottom one. To finish he disassembles the base frame and the sidebars.

attributes.Transcription: Hello. Thank you for agreeing to take part in our study.
In front of you ,you will see a IKEA bathroom cabinet.
Your test, for now, will be to disassemble it.
